WEBVTT

00:12:59.954 --> 00:13:01.532
stop liking

00:13:01.556 --> 00:13:03.325
and stop sharing.

00:13:03.349 --> 00:13:07.067
Write to the producers,

00:13:07.091 --> 00:13:11.863
editors, station managers and CEOs

00:13:11.887 --> 00:13:14.123
of these news organizations.

00:13:14.147 --> 00:13:19.292
Take note of the advertisers
who support those segments

00:13:19.316 --> 00:13:21.579
and write to their CEOs.

00:13:22.101 --> 00:13:23.748
Because together,

00:13:24.573 --> 00:13:28.650
we can push the media
to act in the interest

00:13:28.674 --> 00:13:31.010
of public safety,